 NC ( net cat):
 =============
	nc is the tool which used to test the service status in remote machine

	telnet and nc are for same purpose

	for telnet which alternative? NC

    which tool is recommended telnet or NC?
		NC

	nc -vz 192.168.145.100 22
	nc -vz remotemachineip  portnumber
				-v verbose
				-z zero packates
	tcp
	udp

using nc we can test both tcp and udp protocol service status